Privacy Policy
Last updated: June 25, 2024
I. Introduction
SuperFun Games respects the privacy of its users and is committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, store, and disclose your personal information when you use our games, websites, or any other services provided by SuperFun Games.
II. Information Collection
When you interact with our services, we may collect the following types of information:
1.
Personal Information:
This includes your name, email address, phone number, and any other information you voluntarily provide to us.
2.
Device Information:
We may collect information about your device, such as IP address, operating system, device model, and browser type.
3.
Gameplay Information:
We collect information about your gameplay, including scores, achievements, and in-game purchases.
4.
Location Information:
If you enable location services, we may collect your approximate location to provide you with localized content and services.
III. Use of Information
We use your personal information for the following purposes:
1.
Providing Services:
To provide you with the games, services, and customer support you request.
2.
Improving Services:
To improve our games and services based on your feedback and usage data.
3.
Personalization:
To customize your gaming experience and provide you with personalized content and recommendations.
4.
Marketing:
To send you promotional materials and offers that may be of interest to you.
IV. Sharing of Information
We may share your personal information with:
1.
Service Providers:
Companies that help us provide our services, such as payment processors and analytics providers.
2.
Legal Obligations:
Government agencies or law enforcement officials if required by law.
3.
Affiliates and Partners:
Companies that we collaborate with for marketing and promotional activities.
V. Storage and Security
We employ security measures to protect your personal information, including encryption, access controls, and regular security audits. However, please note that no system can guarantee absolute security.
VI. Your Rights
You have the right to:
1.Access your personal information.
2.Correct or update your personal information.
3.Request deletion of your personal information.
4.Object to the use of your personal information for marketing purposes.
VII. Children's Privacy
Our services are not intended for children under the age of 13. If we become aware that a child has provided us with personal information without parental consent, we will take steps to delete that information.
VIII. Changes to this Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any significant changes by posting a notice on our website or through our services.
IX. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at ouyangpeng@superfunxgames.com.
By using SuperFun Games' services, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.